//Note: This hub was created by the [http://05command.wikidot.com/maintenance-and-ancillary-staff-team-main#toc5 WikiWalk team] in 2022 for ease of accessing the entries and details of [/forum/t-376556/contest-for-1000 Contest for 1000], which occured in 2011.//
-----
[[div class="img-shadow"]]
[[=image https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp1000contesthub/1000.png]]
[[/div]]

[[size 130%]] **This is the hub for the 2011 Contest for 1000**[[/size]], the very first "kon", as we so affectionately call them now. Having run from July 27th to September 1st 2011, it was a historic event that would set the trend for the coveted X000 slots for decade(s) to come, shifting the site from a "we're close to 1000 SCPs, prune the list" vision, to "we're close to 1000 SCPs, let's grow bigger". More than five thousand SCP articles later[[footnote]]At the time of writing.[[/footnote]], we can't imagine what the Wiki would look like without these contests, and without the hype they bring.

Unlike all the other X000 contests, this one took place in a [/forum/t-376556/contest-for-1000 forum thread], which makes finding information about the contest quite the challenge for the curious reader. As a result, we on Staff decided to make this Hub to keep in line with the modern times, and to make everything easier to find.

[[size larger]]The contest's theme was: ##500000|**Folktales and/or Urban Legends**##[[/size]]
